data.description: This 2 acre property sits right at the entrance of Bouse coming in from Parker. VERY clean manufactured home that is 2 bedroom 2 bath with a split floor plan. Covered patios on both front and back sides. Enjoy the 1 car garage and 2 car covered carport. 1 bedroom travel trailer stays on property for guests or would make a great winter rental. 4 Full RV hook ups total. Backs up against the Bouse Wash for easy access to desert riding. Come take a look today!
